{"tid":1415191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［收到風］唔單止北角，今晚屯門元朗荃灣黑底做野","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:53:02.000Z","uid":259251,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e922375d6c363e031aa1118b726b2ac67dee2602","tid":1415191,"uid":259251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:20:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屯門元朗荃灣</span></span>的街坊及義士準備多些防護裝備！<br />\n<br />\n收到風黑底會做嘢，今次可能仲有頭盔添。<br />\n<br />\n小心人身安全！<br />\n<br />\n整好隊形，小心絲打安全！<br />\n<br />\n我哋人多，多啲用手頭上的野去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">刺</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">亂揮動及扑其實唔夠力+ 容易誤中隊友<br />\n</span><br />\n記住係：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n刺<br />\n刺<br />\n刺</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好英雄主義，一齊上一齊退！<br />\n<br />\n睇住你身邊的隊友！小心佢哋太激動！<br />\n<br />\n唔可以再比黑社會咁臭串！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">自己香港自己守護！</span></span>"},{"pid":"24e9a9cf6232defc53f91a7b7fb8c7097b98e0bb","tid":1415191,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f7572b83c60a7e737102ff49dee4b8d86dc3a179","tid":1415191,"uid":259251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"大家準備多啲都好，唔知道幾時出嚟"},{"pid":"d7889761621c9c342891ee8b7f49b5fbeeca2eb6","tid":1415191,"uid":259251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0cc456821bac84fbf929c3a99fa0e1e1149cec29","tid":1415191,"uid":44055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"未FC，但元朗千色果頭暫時風平浪靜"},{"pid":"29dd6e66be7ab8a959e272ca0839596365e13d87","tid":1415191,"uid":2293